                        <interp inst="t18440506-name-543" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS TUCKER</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at No. 14, Lower North-street. The prisoner is a stranger to me—I sent for no coals—they were not taken in.</p>
